description.plain:
NOTD, pronounced as ‘noted’, is a Swedish pop/EDM music production duo comprised of Tobias Danielsson and Samuel Brandt. The duo is most well known for their Platinum-certified single “I Wanna Know” and Gold-certified single “So Close”.

The duo got their start remixing mainstream pop hits which garnered them an Electronic Music Award for Remix of the Year in 2017 prior to the release of any of their original songs. Upon the release of their second single, the aforementioned “I Wanna Know”, NOTD saw instant success, with the song being their most popular to date.

songs.title_with_featured: Been There Done That (Ft. Tove Styrke)

description.plain:
“Been There Done That” is a single by Swedish production duo NOTD featuring Swedish singer Tove Styrke. It was released on August 24, 2018.

The song explores how even one a member of a past relationship wants it to work out, the narrator knows that they’ve “been there, done that,” and that the relationship will have the same issues that it had in the past.
